oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Interview and Performance - Dierks Bentley - 2016-03-12
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Interview with and performance by Dierks Bentley from the CMA Theater at the Country Music Hall of Fame and Museum on March 12, 2016. In support of the exhibit Dierks Bentley: Every Mile A Memory.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:creator: Dierks Bentley;
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dcterms:tableOfContents: Interview conducted by Peter Cooper. Performances include; What Was I Thinkin' -- Come A Little Closer -- Free And Easy Down The Road I Go -- Up On The Ridge -- Am I The Only One -- I Hold On -- Drunk On A Plane -- Freedom -- Somewhere On A Beach. Accompanied by Jon Randall Stewart.
